                <p>Our Vision: To create a sustainable future by revolutionizing waste management practices.</p>
                <p>Our Mission: To develop innovative solutions and raise awareness for effective waste management, contributing to a cleaner environment.</p>
                <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
                <div class="team-section">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="/images/me.jpeg" alt="Kethavath Shanker">
